casebody.data:
Thursday, January 28, 1999

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

98-1302. Disciplinary Counsel v. Sweeney.

Upon consideration of respondent’s motion for leave to file additional factual information,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for leave to file additional factual information be, and hereby is, denied.

Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent.
